description: Gets a list of tags associated with a specified resource. Amazon Q Business applications and data sources can have tags associated with them.

parameters.name: resourceARN
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Amazon Q Business application or data source to get a list of tags for.

nested_items.name: tags
nested_items.description: A list of tags associated with the Amazon Q Business application or data source.

nested_items.name: key
nested_items.description: The key for the tag. Keys are not case sensitive and must be unique for the Amazon Q Business application or data source.

nested_items.name: value
nested_items.description: The value associated with the tag. The value may be an empty string but it can't be null.
